===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''titration''' (titrations)
#{{chemistry}} the [[determination]] of the [[concentration]] of some [[substance]] in a [[solution]] by [[slowly]] [[adding]] [[measured]] [[amount]]s of some other [[substance]] (normally using a [[burette]]) until a [[reaction]] is shown to be [[complete]], for instance by the [[colour]] [[change]] of an [[indicator]]

